        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/place/1"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>The total number of bed places (BPs) in tourist accommodations/year in the LAU (Local Administrative Unit) is 5001. The regional (Region) share of total BPs/year is 15.93%. The number of agricultural holdings in the LAU is 2792. The nearest settlement with population over 100000 (km) is 168. In this region protected areas are present.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


