        <ontology:hasDescription>The primary sector share of total employment/year [Province] is 5.15%. The secondary sector share of total employment/year [Province] is 29.20%. The tertiary sector share of total employment/year [Province] is 63.69%. The primary sector share of total employment/year [Region] is 2.75%. The secondary sector share of total employment/year [Region] is 21.82%. The tertiary sector share of total employment/year [Region] is 75.43%.  </ontology:hasDescription>
